Name: PyMedTermino
Version: 0.3
Summary: Medical Terminologies for Python: SNOMED CT, ICD10, MedDRA, CDF, UMLS and VCM icons
Home-page: http://www.lesfleursdunormal.fr/static/informatique/pymedtermino/index_en.html
